CustomField.description: If checked for a billable Expense, this means that the portion of the Expense amount specified in the Incurred Tax field is not billable. (This is separate from and in addition to any amount in the Non-Billable Incurred Amount field).
CustomField.inlineHelpText: If checked for a billable Expense, this means that the portion of the Expense amount specified in the Incurred Tax field is not billable. (This is separate from and in addition to any amount in the Non-Billable Incurred Amount field).
CustomField.label: Incurred Tax Non-Billable
